Class GroupBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ami.mse.ucms.groups.GroupBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Named(value="groupBean")
@ViewAccessScoped
public class GroupBean
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The Class GroupBean. Contains methods for save the instance of Group and methods that supports the viewing of group details, searching for Group and editing one.
